sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Pengguna
    participant Halaman as HalamanDashboard
    participant Controller as DashboardController
    participant Service as DashboardService
    participant Produk as Product
    participant Transaksi as Transaction

    Pengguna->>+Halaman: Buka halaman dashboard
    Halaman->>+Controller: index(period)
    Controller->>Controller: Tentukan periode (default: bulan ini)
    
    Controller->>+Service: getAset()
    Service-->>-Controller: Total aset & detail
    Controller->>+Service: getBarangRusak(start, end)
    Service-->>-Controller: Barang rusak periode
    Controller->>+Service: getPoAktif(start, end)
    Service-->>-Controller: PO aktif periode
    Controller->>+Service: getHutang()
    Service-->>-Controller: Hutang tempo & detail
    Controller->>+Service: getKategoriTerlaris(start, end)
    Service-->>-Controller: Kategori terlaris
    Controller->>+Service: getChartData()
    Service-->>-Controller: Data chart mingguan & bulanan

    Controller->>+Transaksi: Transaksi terbaru (5 data)
    Transaksi-->>-Controller: Data transaksi
    Controller->>+Produk: Dead stock (stok>0, 6 bln tidak bergerak)
    Produk-->>-Controller: Data dead stock
    Controller->>+Produk: Stok menipis (stok<5, 3 data)
    Produk-->>-Controller: Data stok menipis

    Controller-->>Halaman: Kirim semua data dashboard
    Halaman-->>Pengguna: Tampilkan widget aset, PO, hutang, chart, stok menipis

    Pengguna->>Halaman: Ubah filter periode
    Halaman->>+Controller: index(period baru)
    Controller-->>-Halaman: Data dashboard diperbarui
    Halaman-->>Pengguna: Tampilkan widget sesuai periode
